@startuml
title Diagrama de Secuencia - Crear Recurso
actor "Administrador" as Admin
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "API (FastAPI)" as API
participant "RecursoService" as Service
participant "RecursoRepository" as Repo
database "Base de Datos" as DB
Admin -> FE: Clic en "Nuevo Recurso"
activate FE
FE --> Admin: Mostrar Formulario
Admin -> FE: Ingresa datos (Código, Nombre) y Guardar
FE -> API: POST /recursos (RecursoCreate JSON)
activate API
API -> Service: crear_recurso(recurso_create)
activate Service
Service -> Repo: create(recurso_model)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: INSERT INTO recursos ...
activate DB
DB --> Repo: ID nuevo recurso
deactivate DB
Repo --> Service: Recurso (con ID)
deactivate Repo
Service --> API: RecursoResponse
deactivate Service
API --> FE: 201 Created (Recurso JSON)
deactivate API
FE -> FE: Actualizar Lista / Notificar Éxito
FE --> Admin: Mostrar "Recurso creado correctamente"
deactivate FE
@enduml
